title: TT is not up yet
body:
Has Twisted Treeline been cancelled along with the RGM for this weekend, or is it just going up very late?
At the time of writing this, TT was scheduled to go online 30 minutes ago

Rito plz help

replies.body:
http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/oTA7PnYT-upcoming-changes-to-twisted-treeline-ranked-flex

> We're taking a small step in that direction, by TESTING an expansion of TT Ranked to two nights a week, but reducing the amount of hours that the queue is active per day. Starting this week TT Ranked Flex will be available:
> 
> Thursday: 5:00pm - 0:00am AEDT (7 hours)
> Friday: 5:00pm - 0:00am AEDT (7 hours)
